Class EventAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.ling.brat.AbstractAnnotation
      • gov.nih.nlm.ling.brat.RelationAnnotation
        • gov.nih.nlm.ling.brat.EventAnnotation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Annotation, java.lang.Comparable<Annotation>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PredicationAnnotation

    public class EventAnnotation
extends RelationAnnotation
    The class to represent an event annotation. An event is essentially a complex semantic object analogous to a predicate-argument structure. It extends RelationAnnotation, by requiring a predicate.
    Author:
    Halil Kilicoglu
